beginning, containing an area of TWENTY SIX THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED SEVENTY ONE (26,971) square meters, more or less.

All corners referred to are marked OLD PS are Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15×50 cms., bearing is true, date of survey November 12, 2003 and was approved on December 11, 2003.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 24 TH day of FEB, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

